HEADWORD: Willemite
<hw>Wil"lem*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Willem</ets> I., king of the Netherlands.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>A silicate of zinc, usually occurring massive and of a greenish
yellow color, also in reddish crystals (troostite) containing
manganese.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

